(3861, 257, '_service_detail_detail_content_1_detail_content1', 'field_62abee9d956f2'),
(3862, 257, 'service_detail_detail_content_1_detail_content1_0_detail_content2_content', '\r\nOne of the most widely used digital advertising is Google Ads. You can set up marketing through Google Ads in such a way that it can be right on target. Usually, these ad settings are formulated based on keywords, location, language, age, and so on.\r\n'),
(3863, 257, '_service_detail_detail_content_1_detail_content1_0_detail_content2_content', 'field_62abeeaa956f3'),
(3864, 257, 'service_detail_detail_content_1_detail_content1_1_detail_content2_content', 'Apart from Google Ads, you can also place digital ads on various other platforms. Such as YouTube Ads, Instagram Ads, Facebook Ads, Twitter Ads, and many more.'),
(3865, 257, '_service_detail_detail_content_1_detail_content1_1_detail_content2_content', 'field_62abeeaa956f3'),
(3866, 257, 'service_detail_detail_content_2_detail_title', 'Social Media Marketing'),
(3867, 257, '_service_detail_detail_content_2_detail_title', 'field_62abeae060c95'),
(3868, 257, 'service_detail_detail_content_2_detail_description', 'The next type of marketing that is often done by online marketing services is social media marketing. As the name implies, this form of promotion utilizes social media. Some social media platforms that are often used are Facebook, Instagram, Twitter, and so on.'),
(3869, 257, '_service_detail_detail_content_2_detail_description', 'field_62abeb0460c96'),
(3870, 257, 'service_detail_detail_content_2_detail_content1', '1'),
(3871, 257, '_service_detail_detail_content_2_detail_content1', 'field_62abee9d956f2'),
(3872, 257, 'service_detail_detail_content_2_detail_content1_0_detail_content2_content', 'In addition to marketing through social media, you can also improve your business by managing social media accounts. This process will be further implemented through social media management, which includes managing your business accounts and content.'),
(3873, 257, '_service_detail_detail_content_2_detail_content1_0_detail_content2_content', 'field_62abeeaa956f3'),
(3874, 257, 'service_detail_detail_content_3_detail_title', 'Email Marketing'),
(3875, 257, '_service_detail_detail_content_3_detail_title', 'field_62abeae060c95'),
(3876, 257, 'service_detail_detail_content_3_detail_description', 'If you have ever received an email containing a certain product or brand promotion, then you are getting email marketing. Email marketing is indeed one of the online promotional tools that are widely used professionally. '),
(3877, 257, '_service_detail_detail_content_3_detail_description', 'field_62abeb0460c96'),
(3878, 257, 'service_detail_detail_content_3_detail_content1_0_detail_content_title', 'Choose a Trusted Digital Marketing Service'),
(3879, 257, '_service_detail_detail_content_3_detail_content1_0_detail_content_title', 'field_62abeb3f60c98'),
(3880, 257, 'service_detail_detail_content_3_detail_content1_0_detail_content_content', ' Digital marketing and promotion or online marketing does have various advantages that you can take advantage of. In order for you to get the maximum benefits, you need to apply the right strategy and type of digital marketing.  There are various things you need to consider when creating an effective digital marketing strategy. The same goes for when you want to choose which type of promotion to use to boost your business.  For that, you can entrust your promotion and marketing in the digital realm to Next Innovations Digital Services in Myanmar Supported by professionals who are experts in their fields, Next Innovations is ready to help improve your business through online marketing.  With Next Innovations, you can utilize a variety of services that are suitable and appropriate for your business or company. Starting from digital advertising, social media management, website optimization and SEO implementation, and many more.   So, trust your business and brand development to Next Innovations Digital Marketing services. Get more information via info@next-innovations.ltd and our professional team is ready to help you. Next Innovations , your trusted digital marketing services.'),
